OL,6,FAround 195 homes will be created with
OL,7,Fa quarter sold as affordable but
OL,8,FHousing Minister Deputy Sam Mezec
OL,9,Fwants all of them to be offered as
OL,10,Fsuch.
OL,12,FHe says: "I've never been supportive
OL,13,Fof this scheme and I've never been in
OL,14,Ffavour of using publically owned land
OL,15,Ffor homes that aren't designated as
OL,16,Faffordable, but the permission's been
OL,17,Fgranted so we are where we are."
