OL,3,CControversial plans for almost 200 new
OL,4,Cflats approved on appeal
OL,6,FDeputy Mezec has told ITV News that he
OL,7,Fwill look to work with developers on
OL,8,Foptions such as shared-equity and
OL,9,Fdeposit-saving schemes to make them
OL,10,Fmore accessible for people who would
OL,11,Fnot otherwise be able to buy these
OL,12,Fproperties.
OL,14,FConcerns had been raised.
OL,16,FThe plans will see the former military
OL,17,Fbarracks site turned into 139 one to
OL,18,Fthree-bed apartments with a basement
OL,19,Fcar park for 70 vehicles and 220
OL,20,Fbicycles.
