OL,4,Cflats approved on appeal
OL,6,FThe development will also now include
OL,7,Fa new children's playground and public
OL,8,Ftoilets, along with reassurances for
OL,9,Fthe listed barracks to offer amenities
OL,10,Ffor the benefit of residents.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, the Hotel Savoy plans will
OL,13,Fsee the site demolished and replaced
OL,14,Fwith 53 one-to-four-bed apartments.
OL,16,FPosting on X, formerly Twitter,
OL,17,FJersey's previous Housing Minister and
OL,18,FSt Helier Deputy David Warr called the
OL,19,Fapprovals "fantastic news".
