OL,6,FConnetable Jackson said: "The
OL,7,Fconditions set out will secure the
OL,8,Fprovision of affordable housing in the
OL,9,Fdevelopments, and improvements to the
OL,10,Fsustainable transport network and
OL,11,Fpublic realm.
OL,13,F"The schemes will yield just under 200
OL,14,Fmuch-needed homes for the island, and
OL,15,Fin the case of South Hill, make much
OL,16,Fbetter use of a disused site."
